 2. the indian is the journalist##1
 3. the egyptian is on the right of the manager##1
 4. the malaysian is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the colombian is between the canadian and the photographer##2
 6. the indian is on the right of the chinese##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the malaysian is on the left of the photographer##1
 9. the canadian is on the far right##1
10. the engineer is on the right of the musician##1
11. the american is the accountant##1
12. the engineer is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the journalist##1
14. the canadian is the person drinking water##1
15. the chinese is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
