 9. the musician is the person watching action movies##1
10. the dancer is the person eating pumpkin##1
11. the person watching animation movies is the dressmaker##1
12. the person eating banana is the manager##1
13. the analyst is on the far right##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching drama movies##2
15. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
