10. the person driving the tram is the ranch-style house##1
11. the doctor is on the right of the firefighter##1
12. the person driving the subway is between the doctor and the analyst##2
13. the wooden house is on the right of the doctor##1
14. the person driving the airplane is the art-deco house##1
15. the freelancer is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
