7 different pets are kept: cat, frog, hedgehog, lizard, mouse, pony, rabbit
 1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the security-guard##1
 2. the security-guard is on the left of the social-worker##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
 4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the chef##1
 5. the librarian is the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the cat is between the dancer and the social-worker##2
 7. the chef is in the middle##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the person traveling to london##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
11. the analyst is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the analyst is the owner of the hedgehog##1
13. the owner of the frog is on the right of the chef##1
14. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
15. the person traveling to london is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |   4    |      5      |       6        |       7       |
